7-09-07T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬原來貓奴</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我養緊兩隻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55557bfd7ec0ce7a603c883286112d629e057d8","tid":391224,"uid":34289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"f1ec207e230ac85695e4d41e9069eefabaefb2b2","tid":391224,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我唔明 執貓點解一定要帶左佢去睇獸醫先<br />\n我本身有隻貓   7月頭果時執左隻小貓   而家咪又係正正常常.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW  我估計小貓貓3個月大  呢個時間去打疫苗唔會太遲呀可?</blockquote><br />\n其實睇獸醫係我約佢出黎既籍口  想再勸佢諗清楚   我睇佢兩個月都唔知有冇  得手掌咁大隻架咋"},{"pid":"7968bd62a3936f21218d9978036ae32c1caa8989","tid":391224,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬原來貓奴</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我養緊兩隻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n領養架 比人reject過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e7239fe46bc133f114a72366fdb8869323e898","tid":391224,"uid":63515,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"唔通你見人無錢養個仔，你又走去叫人送比人養或孤兒院咩<br />\n<br />\n佢養得自已會諗架啦"},{"pid":"dabcdf6cf2c06638ff64be926aef7f1da11618b9","tid":391224,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通你見人無錢養個仔，你又走去叫人送比人養或孤兒院咩<br />\n<br />\n佢養得自已會諗架啦</blockquote><br />\n我岩先問佢打算點 <br />\n佢答我 唔知 好亂<br />\n講到隻貓係我質比佢咁"},{"pid":"d1db8b0ce7d41a4767c20bfd7f144e5415faf39d","tid":391224,"uid":12415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"樓主養掂條女，條女養掂隻貓咪得囉"},{"pid":"2e30541e2b2a02f20d1e1892d246cf6b3ac8de5d","tid":391224,"uid":113422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我唔明 執貓點解一定要帶左佢去睇獸醫先<br />\n我本身有隻貓   7月頭果時執左隻小貓   而家咪又係正正常常.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW  我估計小貓貓3個月大  呢個時間去打疫苗唔會太遲呀可?</blockquote><br />\n要檢查下隻貓有冇病有冇受左傷 有時隻貓可能感染左病毒但未病發 <br />\n貓出左世戒左奶啲抗體好快就冇 打針都係預防佢有機會感染到某啲病毒 通常都係3個月大之前就打3針<br />\n之後每年都再補打針同杜蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}